name: TheNFT #1752/1799
description: The SEC issued an 18-page investigative report about TheDAO. The report concluded that, DAO Tokens, a Digital Asset, were securities. Each page of the pfd has been converted into bitmaps, then broken up into 100 tiles. Each tile is minted as an NFT, with 1 original TheDAO token wrapped inside. This is page 18, tile 53 (serial numbers start from 0)
